  <brief_title>Effects of an Intervention Program Based on Pain Education in Patients With Chronic Pelvic Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Controlled Study of the Effects of an Intervention Program Based on Pain Education in Pain Activity Patterns and Brain Connectivity in Patients With Chronic Pelvic Pain by Magnetic Resonance Images</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
